Okweyongerayongerayongera kw'obulwadde bw'obwongo (KOVID-19) mu European Union/European Equature Economic ne United Kingdom, 1 Jjanwali okutuuka Maaki 2020
Omuwendo gw'abantu abakwatibwa endwadde y'obwongo (KOVID-19) gulaga embeera y'emu mu Bulaaya/Ebugwanjuba bw'ensi mu Bulaaya ne mu United Kingdom, nga bwe kiragiddwa ku ggwanga mu ngeri ey'enjawulo, nnawookeera w'ekirwadde kya covirus we kyeyongera buli lukya mu nsi yonna.
Okusinziira ku bye tulabye okuva e Italy, ensi, amalwaliro n’ebitongole ebijjanjaba abalwadde ennyo byandyeyongedde okweteekerateekera abalwadde abali mu covid-19 abajja okwetaaga obuyambi bw’eby’obujjanjabi, era n’abo abeetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi.
Nga 31 Ddesemba 2019, waaliwo obulwadde bw’amawuggwe obuyitibwa pneumonia obw’obulwadde obutamanyiddwa mu kibuga Wuhan, ekiri mu ssaza ly’e Hubei, mu China.
Nga 9 Jjanwali 2020, ekitongole ekya China Center for Disease Control and Prevention kyagamba nti ekika ky'ekiwuka kino kiyitibwa coronavirus.
Okuva bwe kiri nti obulwadde obuva mu SARS-COV2 buyitiddwa obulwadde bw'obwongo (COVID-19).
Obujulizi bulaga nti 80 ku buli kikumi eky'abantu abalina covid-19 balina obulwadde obukkakkanya, kwe kugamba, obulwadde bw'okussa.
Mu bijawo 14%, covid-19 efuna obulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'okwetaaza abasawo ng'ate 6 ku buli kikumi abasigaddeyo balwala obulwadde obw'amaanyi obwetaaga okulabirirwa ennyo.
Omuwendo gw'abalwadde abafa olw'eddwaliro lya COVID-19 gubalinga ka 4 ku buli kikumi.
Mu kunoonyereza kuno, twekenneenya omuwendo gw'abo abali mu Covid-19 mu buli European Union/European Economic Aquares (EU/EEA) ne mu United Kingdom (UK) era ne tugeraageranyizibwa ku ssaza ly'e Hubei mu China.
Era tuyinza okugeraageranya omuwendo gw'abo abali mu EU/EEA ne UK ku muwendo gw'abo abaliwo mu nsi zino ne mu Italy mu 31/15 Maaki 2020.
Obulumbaganyi mu nsi za EU/EEA ne UK bulina kye bukola ku kiwandikiro oba ku kiwandikiro
Oluvannyuma lw’okutuuka mu China, COVID-19 yabunyisibwa mu bitundu ebirala eby’ensi era n’ekirwadde ekiyitibwa KOVID - 19 mu nsi yonna kyabuna mu bitundu ebirala.
Nga 11 Maaki 2020, Omuduumizi w’Ekibiina ky’eby’Obulamu eky’Ensi Yonna yagamba nti, omuwendo gw’abantu abalwadde oguyitibwa COVID-19 gwasaasaana.
Mu kabangali 5 Maaki Eurosurveillance 2020, Spitari et al. Lipoota ekwata ku nnawookeera w'e Bulaaya eyasooka okukakasibwa COVOVID-19 okusinziira ku nkola y'ekitongole kya WHO.
Mu kibiina ky’EU/EEA, emisango esatu egyasooka okukakasibwa gyaweebwa Bufalansa nga Jjanwali 24 2020 mu bantu abaava mu Wuhan, mu ssaza ly’e Hubei, China.
Mu ngeri y'emu nga 15 Maaki 2020, omuwendo gw'obulwadde bwa covid-19 gwalabibwa mu nsi zonna 30 ez'omu EU/EEA ne mu United Kingdom (UEA), wakati wa 31 Ddesemba 2019 ne ku olwo, era nga 39,768 be baafa, ate nga 1,727 baafa nga 17,750 n'abantu 1,41 okuva mu Italy yokka.
Okufuna omuwendo ogw'enyongeza ogw'abo abakwatibwa COVID-19
Mu European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control (ECDC), omuwendo gw’abalwadde abakwatibwa COVID-19 okwetooloola ensi yonna gwe bafuna okuva eri ab’obuyinza mu buli nsi nga Ministry of Health, ab'obuyinza mu by'obulamu mu nsi ne mu WHO, gulongoosebwa buli lunaku nga 8:00 a.m.
Ebintu bino byakozesebwa okukebera enkola eya covid-19 mu EU/EEA ne mu UK, era ne bigeraageranyizibwa ku ebyo ebibeera mu Italy.
Okuteeberezebwa kw'obulwadde buno obukolebwa ku KOVID-19, twabalirira obubonero bw'enyongeza obwa kyebuva bukendeera mu nnaku 14 eza COVID-19, mu buli EU/EEA ne UK, mu kiseera kya 1 Mutarama/19 Maaki 2020.
Era twalaga omuwendo mungi ogw'obujulizi obulaga buli ggwanga nga Maaki 2020 8:00 a.m. bwe gugeraageranyizibwa n'ogwa Italy mu bbanga lya 31 Jjanwali -15 Maaki 2020.
Enkyukakyuka mu KOVID-19 mu nsi z'EU/EEA ne UK
Omuwendo gw'abo abakwatibwa COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne UK byaddirira omuwendo gw'abo abakwatibwa olw'ennaku 14 ez'enkanvu mu kiseera kino.
Omuwendo gw'ebibiina ebikola EU/EEA ne UK okutwalira awamu, omuwendo gw'abo abakwatibwa okuva ku KOVID okutuuka ku 21 Ogwokutaano gwatandika okweyongera ate oluvannyuma ne gweyongera nnyo ng’ogwa 28 Ogweebiri 2020.
Kino kyakubirizibwa nnyo okweyongera kw'omuwendo gw'obujulizi okuva mu Italy, naye ensi endala zonna ez'omu EU/EEA ne UK nazo zaalaga omuwendo gw'abo abeeyongera obungi mu COVID-19.
Olupapula 2 lulaga omuwendo gw'abalwadde abali mu KOVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne UK bwe bigeraageranyizibwa n'ebyo ebiri mu Italy mu kiseera ekya 31 Jjanwali-15 Maaki 2020.
Kiraga nti, nga bwe kyali nga Maaki 8: 00 a.m., ensi endala 15 ez’omu EU/EEA n’EK zaali zimaze okuwerera ddala omuwendo gw’abalwadde abalinga Italy wiiki ssatu zokka oba ntono nnyo nga tezinnabaawo.
Ebyo bye tuzudde biraga nti omuwendo gw'abo abategeezebwa ekibiina kya EU/EEA ne UK gweyongera buli lukya.
Okunoonyereza okwo kulaga nti mu nsi zonna, endwadde eyo yeeyongera bweyongezi okulinnya ku sipiidi y’emu.
Kino kyeyoleka mu nsi wadde nga ziri mu mitendera egy'enjawulo, nga n'ennyinnyonnyola z'eby'obulamu ez'enjawulo mu nsi era ne mu ngeri ez'enjawulo nga zigoberera enkola ez'enjawulo ez'okulonda abalwadde abalina okukeberebwa okukakasa nti ekika ky'obulwadde kimaze okukwatibwa, nga mw'otwalidde n'okukebera obujanjabi.
Ng’omwaka gwa Maaki 2020 gwakatandika, abasawo mu bitundu bya Italy ebyakosebwa ennyo baayogera ku mbeera eyaliwo ng’abasawo 10 ku buli kikumi abaalina okulabirirwa mu ddwaliro ne mu mikutu gy’eby’empuliziganya balaga nti amalwaliro n’ebitongole ebijjanjaba abo abali mu bitundu ebyo baali beetaagiddwa nnyo.
Ekiragiro kino kikebera ebitundu ebiri mu EU/EEEA ebiri wansi w'obulwadde 6% n'ebitundu 1% nga buli kimu kiragiddwa (amannya agatalagibwa).
Kyokka, basaanidde okukuŋŋaanyizibwa mu ngeri ey’enjawulo basobole okukakasa nti omuwendo gw’abo abakwatibwa gulimu omuwendo gwa bajulizi n’omuwendo gw’abo abafa.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu 2010 -11 kwalaga nti mu Bulaaya waliwo ebitundu 29,2 eby’okulabirirwa abalwadde abalwadde ennyo.
Kino kitegeeza nti ensi ziyinza okuba n’eby’obugagga ebisukka ku Italy era n’ebitanda ku buli bantu 100,000 mu 2010 -11.
Engeri ez'okulabirako ezikwataganyizibwa n'obukkusi bw'eby'obujjanjabi mu buli ggwanga EU/EEA ne UK ey'obulwadde obw'eddwaliro obucaase mu ddwaliro era n'obulwadde obw'ekika kya COVID-19, ebireetebwawo ebireetebwawo ebireetebwa abalwadde ennyo, biri mu ngeri ey'omukaaga ey'okunoonyereza okukwata ku ECDC mu ngeri ey'enjawulo ku kika kya CHOVID-19.
Okuva bwe kiri nti obujulizi bubunye mu bitundu ebimu eby'omu EU/EEA ne UK, era nga n'amalwaliro n'ebitongole ebijjanjaba abalwadde ennyo bisobola okukwasa obusawo bw'abalwadde bangi, obubaka obukwata ku bibamba n'ebitanda ebirwadde eby'abalwadde ennyo bwetaaga nnyo okufunibwa mu bitongole ebigabanyi ebiri mu bitundu bya EU/EEA okusobola okufuna emiwendo 2 (NUTS - 2).
Ebyo bye tulabye okuva mu Yitale ne mu nsi endala biraga nti nnawookeera w’omutawaana gwa COVID-19 gweyongedde nnyo mu EU/EEA ne mu UK.
Amawanga, amalwaliro n'ebitongole ebijjanjaba abalwadde ennyo mu ngeri eyo birina okweteekateeka okweyongera okutambuza abantu mu SARS-CoV-2 era n'okweyongera kw'omuwendo gw'abalwadde abalina covid-19 abeetaaga obuyambi bw'eby'obujjanjabi, gamba ng'abo ababeera mu bitundu bya Italy ebikoseddwa.
Nga bwe kiragiddwa mu kunoonyereza okwakakolebwa gye buvuddeko awo, enkola ey'okusalako akabi, ey'amangu era ey'okwanguyiriza, kikulu nnyo okulemesa okusaasaana kwa SARS-COV2, nga n'enkola ey'okusalamu enzivuunula okuva ku kukozesa enkola ey'okutumbula obukwasiro ereetebwawo, ng'omuwendo gw'abalwadde bwe gusuubira teguyinza kusobozesa abakola eby'okusalawo oba amalwaliro okukitegeera, okukkiriza n'okutuukana n'ebyo ebiyinza okukolebwa nga bukyali bukya.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa kungi era kulaga engeri obulwadde obwo gye buyambamu abantu okukendeeza ku bulwadde obuva ku bulwadde obwo.
Amawanga mangi gayinza okwongera ku ngeri gye gayinza okukendeeza ku kupikirizibwa okwa SaRS-CoV-2 era n'okukendeeza ku kunyigirizibwa kw'eby'obujjanjabi.
Bwe kityo, kiyinzika okuba nti ebibiina by’eby’obujjanjabi eby’omu nsi endala birina abalwadde bangi abeetaaga okulabirirwa obulungi mu nnaku oba wiiki ezijja.
Obulwadde bwa coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), obuva ku bulwadde bw'amawuggwe (SARS) 2 (SARS-CoV2), busse abantu abasukka mu 3,000 era bwakwata abantu abasukka mu 800,000 mu China ne mu bitundu ebirala mu nsi, ne kiviirako abantu emitawaana egy'amaanyi.
Okufaananako akawuka akayitibwa homologous, SARS-COV, akaaleetera SARS mu nkumi n'enkumi z'abantu mu 2003, akawuka akayitibwa SARS-COV kayinza okusaasaana mu ngeri y'emu era n'obuwuka obwo ne buleetera n'obubonero obufaananako.
Kyokka, omuwendo gw’abakazi abafa mutono okusinga SARS, era ekyo kikosa nnyo bannamukadde okusinga abavubuka n’abasajja okusinga abakazi.
Olw’okweyongerayongerayongera kw’ebitabo ebikwata ku bulwadde obubaawo, ekitundu kino kinoonyereza ku nsonga eno egenda ekolebwa mu bwangu ddala mu kiseera ekituufu.
Tujja kwogera ku nkola ereetebwawo obulwadde, estronomy, enzijanjaba gye bukola, obukessi, enzijanjaba gye bujja, n'obusobozi bw'okubuziyiza.
Wadde nga wakyaliyo ebibuuzo bingi ebyetaaga okuddibwamu, tusuubira nti okwejjukanya kuno kujja kuyamba mu kutegeera n’okumalawo obulwadde obwo obw’akabi.
Embaga ey’Oluyimba nga Jjanwali 25, 2020 efuuse ekintu ekitabangawo era ekitayinza kwerabirwa eri Abakyayina bonna abaakubirizibwa okusigala mu nnyumba okumala ennaku eyo yonna era okumala wiiki eziwerako oluvannyuma lw’obulwadde obw’akabi ennyo.
Akawuka ako kakwata nnyo ku corogues corovirus (COV) akaaleeta obulwadde bw'amawuggwe mu 2003; bwe kityo, kaayitibwa SARS-CoV-2 Akakiiko k'eby'obulamu obw'ensi yonna (WHO) nga 11 Febwali 2020, era obulwadde obukimu bwatuumibwa CoV Disease-19 (COVOVID-19).
Akawumpuli ako kaatandika mu Wuhan, China, era kaabuna mangu mu nsi yonna ne mu bitundu ebirala nga 50 okwetooloola ensi yonna.
Mu Maaki 2, 2020, akawuka ako kaaviirako abantu abasukka mu 800,000 okukwatibwa, era abalwadde abasukka mu 40,000 be baasumululwa era n’abalwadde abasukka mu 3,000 abaafa.
WHO erabula nti KUVID-19 gwe "Mulabe wa gavumenti 1" era ayinza okuba ow’amaanyi okusinga ebikolwa bya bannalukalala.
Okusinziira ku PoubMud (http://www.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu myezi egitawera ebiri, empapula ezisukka mu 200 ze zifulumidde ku COVID-19 nga mw'otwalidde n'ebyo ebikwata ku nkola y'obulwadde, estrodemiology, okunoonyereza, n'okujjanjaba okuva ku Jjanwali 7, 2020 ebyakakasa omuwendo gw'obulwadde obw'omusokero.
Okwejjukanya kuno okugezaako okuwumbawumbako okunoonyereza mu kifo ekippya ekikulaakulanye amangu.
Buli lwe kiba kisoboka, tugezeeko okugeraageranya COVID-19 ku SARS n'obulwadde obulala obuva mu coV, obulwadde bw'okussa mu kampewo mu Buwalabu mu 2012.
Era tujja kwekenneenya bye tuyize ku bikwata ku kuziyiza n’okuteeberezebwa kw’obulwadde era n’ebibuuzo ebirala ebikyali eby’amangu.
Kirowoozebwa nti obuwuka obwo buleetera abantu okufuna obuwuka obuleeta obuwuka obusirikitu nga 15 ku buli kikumi ku buli kikumi.
Kyokka, mu kyasa kino, tusanzemu abantu bangi abakwatibwa endwadde emirundi ebiri, kwe kugamba, SARS-COV ne MBERS, ekyaviirako nnawookeera mu China mu 2003 ne Saudi Buwalabu mu 2012.
N'olwekyo, okukwatibwa kw' Covid-19 kwe kw'okusatu okwaliwo mu byafaayo by'abantu.
Nga bwe kiragibwa mu ntaana z’emitiini 1,1, ebibinja by’amawuka ag’obusimu agayitibwa pneumonia ebyali bisimbye ensibuko yaabyo nga Ddesemba 31, 2019 okutuuka ku kitongole ky’eby’obulamu eky’omu China ekiyitibwa China National Says Commis.
Oluvannyuma lw’ennaku musanvu ab’ekibiina ekyo baateebwa.
Nga Jjanwali 15, 2020 omusango gw’okutta ogwasooka okuva mu Wuhan gwasalibwawo.
Mu kiseera ekyo, kawumpuli yabuna mangu mu bibuga eby’omuliraano, mu masaza, ne mu nsi endala.
Nga Jjanwali 20, abasawo baaleeta alipoota nti obulwadde bw'abantu bwasobola okutambuza obulamu bw'abantu.
Nga Jjanwali 23, ekibuga ky’e Wuhan kyaggalwawo era eby’entambula byonna ebyakozesebwanga abantu byayimirira.
Nga Jjanwali 24 okunoonyereza okwasooka okukwata ku bulwadde buno kwalaga nti, ku bantu 41 abaalina obulwadde obwakakasibwa, 21 bokka be baali boogerako mu katale k’eby’ennyanja akayitibwa Wuhan, akaali katwalibwa ng’ekifo akatandikirwamu obulwadde obwo okuva mu nsolo etamanyiddwa.
Nga Jjanwali 30, ekibiina ky'ensi yonna kyalangirira obulwadde obw'omutawaana mu nsi yonna.
Alipoota eno we yatuukira, obulwadde buno bumaze okusaasaana mu China ne mu nsi endala nga 50 okwetooloola ensi yonna (Fig.2).
Embeera egenda yeeyongera okuzibuwala, obunene n’amaanyi g’oyo akwatiddwa nnawookeera biba bikyali bya kumalibwawo.
Nga Febwali 11, 2020, okunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku balwadde 8,866 nga mwe muli n'abalwadde 4,021 abakkirizisa COVOID-19, kwalaga olugero olupya olw'obulwadde buno (http:/mp.weixin.q.com/s/UlBi-HHHPXX1qHHA2bda).
SARS-CoV-2 abantu ab'emyaka egy'enjawulo baakwatibwa, naye okusingira ddala nga ba myaka 30-65.
Kumpi kimu kya kubiri (47.7%) ku bantu abaalina obulwadde obwo baali basussa mu myaka 50, nga batono nnyo abaali basussa emyaka 20 egy’obukulu, ate nga 14 bokka be baalina obulwadde obwo nga ba wansi w’emyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 Kano kakwata abasajja abangi (0.31 oba 1000,000) okusinga abakazi (0.27 oba 1000,000).
COVID-19 okusingira ddala zaali zikulaakulanye mu bitundu by’omu Hubei.
KUVID-19 okutwalira awamu kyatwalanga ennaku nga 5 okuva lwe kyatandika okukeberebwa.
Okutwalira awamu, abantu baafukanga ebiwaawaatiro mu nnaku 4.8 (3.0-7.2).
Omuntu okutwalira awamu yamalanga ennaku 9.5 okuva ku ntandikwa okutuuka ku kufa.
