Epidemiological ebyafaayo: (1) Ebyafaayo eby'okutambula oba eby'okusula mu kibuga kya Wuhan ne mu bifo ebirala ebiriraanyewo, oba abantu abalala abaali bakwatiddwako obulwadde bwa covid-19 mu nnaku 14 eziyise ng'obubonero tebunnabalukawo. (2) Ebyafaayo ebikwata ku sipiidi ya ARS-CoV-2 (yalimu okukeberebwa kwa asidi y'ekika); (3) Ebyafaayo eby'okukolagana n'abalwadde abalina omusujja oba obubonero bw'empewo okuva mu kibuga kya Wuhan ne mu bitundu ebiriraanyewo, oba ebitundu ebirala ebya CHOVID gye kyali kijuliziddwa mu nnaku 14 eziyise nga tekinnabalukawo; (4) ebyafaayo eby'obulwadde obw'omusujja n'obulwadde obw'okussaawanya (672).
Engeri z'obujjanjabi eziragibwa: (1) omusujja n'obubonero bw'empewo; (2) n'obubonero obw'okusiiga ebifaananyi eby'obulwadde bwa coVID-19; (3) omuwendo gw'obutoffaali obweru bwonna bulaga nti obwongo, bukendedde, oba bukendeeza ebbeeyi y'obwongo nga baakatandika.
Ekiragiro kino bwe kizuulibwa, kisinziira ku bujulizi bwonna obw'ekika kya kansa nga buno: (1) PCR esobola okukeberebwa ddala nga SARS-COV-2; (2) viruscensial sequencegential ereedition eya kika kya nviromenti emanyiddwa nga coronorvirus; (3) enzivuunvuunvu eyo eya IgM ne IgGG antibody eya SaRS-CoV-2 mu kukebera kwa serum; oba enkyukakyuka ey'ekyuma ekiwandikiro ekiyitibwa SARS-CoV-PGGENA okuva ku butaka obw'ebika eby'enjawulo okutuuka ku mbeera ey'amaanyi, oba okweyongera mu kiseera eky'okulongoosebwa kw'ekiragiro ekyo waggulu.
Eky’okuba nti mu kiseera kyennyini PCR waaliwo asidi eva mu tulakiti ey’okussa oba mu musaayi (18 Jjanwali 2020) n’eky’okusatu (22 Jjanwali 2020) kyateekebwamu obuwuka obutonotono obuyitibwa nucleic acid.
