Russell Zimmerman, omukulu w’ekitongole ekiyitibwa Australian Retailers Association, yagamba nti abasuubuzi bagezaako okutunda ssente, naye enkiiko y’omu kitundu egaana abaddu ba mmotoka okubatwalira ebiseera.
