b'Anigiotensin akyusa enzyme 2 (ACE2) enzyme eteekebwa ku butoffaali bw’obutoffaali obw’omu mawuggwe, mu misiya gy’omutima, mu nsigo, ne mu byenda.
ACE2 era akendeeza ku muwendo gwa enzyme (ACE) eya anigiotensin-II era n'eyongerezaako Ang(1-7) nga kyesembyeyo okujjanjaba endwadde z'omutima. ACE2 era kye kisobozesa obutoffaali bw'obwongo okubuteeka mu butoffaali bw'obwongo.
Enzyme y’omuntu etera okuyitibwa haCE2.
Enzyme eya agiotensin 2, enzyme, ebaamu ebintu ebikolebwa mu kyuma, ebisangibwa ku ntikko y’obutoffaali bw’enyoti ne ku butoffaali obulala.
protein ACE2 zirimu ekitundu ekiyitibwa N-terminal peptidase M2 era n'eky'ekika kya C-terminalrin renal amino acid.
ACE2 kye kimu ku bintu ebiyitibwa protein proteins, era ebitundu byayo eby’omubiri eby’ebbugumu biri mu butoffaali bw’obutoffaali obuli mu mawuggwe ne mu butoffaali obulala.
Ebitundu ebirala ebiyitibwa ACE2 ebibeeramu enzyme enzyme esangibwa mu bitundu bya transmembrane, era enzyme endala eziyitibwa estase, enzyme eyo evaamu obutundutundu obuyitibwa soluble protein, ne buyingira mu mugga ne buvaamu ekikoomi.
ACE2 kisangibwa mu bitundu ebisinga obungi eby’omubiri: ACE2 eteekebwa ku butoffaali bw’obutoffaali bw’omubiri obw’ekika ky’obutoffaali bw’ekika kya II alveolar, enterine, arterial ne vonous endothelial n’obutoffaali bw’ebinywa mu bitundu by’omubiri ebisinga obungi.
OMULABIRIRO gwa ACE2 mRNA era gusangibwa mu ddagala eriyitibwa cerebral cortex, tririatum, hypothalamus, ne mu bwongo.
Omulimu ogusinga obukulu ogwa ACE2 guba gwa kuwanirira ACE.
ACE agatta hormone I mu cormone ey’okubiri n’agikwataganya n’ekipimo ekiyitibwa agiotensin II.
ACE2 akyusa ekika kya carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenlayanine okuva ku ap-Argtensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) era ne hydrobillator anigiontensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-P-PH).
ACE2 era esobola okugatta omuwendo gwa peptides endala nga mw'otwalidde ne [des-Arg9]bradykin, apelin, neronsin, dynorphin A, ne ghrelin.
ACE2 era afuga enkola ey'okutunda enviiri za amino acid ezitwala SLC6A19 era zenyigiddemu mu ndwadde ya Hartnup.
Ekiragiro ACE2 kye kisinga okukola ng'obutoffaali obuva mu butoffaali bw'omubiri, nga mwe muli HCOV-NL63; SARS-COV (akawuka akaleeta SARS); ne SARS-CoV-2 (akawuka akaleeta CHOVID-19).
Okusingira ddala, ebinywa S1 ebikola protein ebiyitibwa SARS-COV ne SARS-CoV2 bisobola okwegatta ku ACE2 mu butoffaali bw'obutoffaali ne kibuteeka mu kawuka ako ne enzyme enzymes mu butoffaali.
Kino era kyetaagisa primmu enzijanjaba y'emu ey'ekika kya S enerne protease TMPRSS2, enzivvuunula kw'eri kati ng'eddagala eriyinza okuleetera abamu okukekkereza ebitundu by'obutoffaali ne kibayamba okulwanyisa obulwadde obwo.
Kyokka, ebibiina by’abantu ebitendekeddwa awamu n’ebibiina ebikola ku by’obujjanjabi by’omuti oguyitibwa ACE brititor n’eddagala eriyitibwa ARB ebyeyongera mu maaso.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa nga Jjulaayi 11, 2012, kwalaga nti okukozesa enzijanjaba za ACE kyakendeereza ddala 34% ku kabi k'okufuna obulwadde bw'amawuggwe.
Okugatta ku ekyo, ‘ obulwadde bw’amawuggwe bwakendeeza n’obulwadde bw’amawuggwe mu mubiri gw’abalwadde abalwala obulwadde bw’amawuggwe obuyitibwa ACE, naddala abo abaalina obulwadde bw’okusannyalala n’omutima.
Enkola ya ACE ekendeeza ku kufa kw'abo abafa olw'obulwadde bw'amawuggwe, wadde ng'ebyo ebyava mu bulwadde obwo tebyali bya maanyi ng'obulwadde bw'amawuggwe obuyitibwa pneumonia.
Omuntu ayitibwa ACE2 (rhaCE2) alowoozebwa okuba enzijanjaba empya ey'obulwadde bw'amawuggwe, era alabika nga yeeyongera okulongoosa engeri amawuggwe gye gatambulamu n'omukka gwe gassa mu biwaawaatiro by'empewo.
Essaawa emu ku kitundu ky'obulamu bw’omuntu, emala essaawa nga 10 era ng'etandika n'essaawa 30, ng'oggyeko ekyo essaawa 24 ze zikola.
Okunoonyereza okutali kumu kulaga nti erhaCE2 eyinza okuganyula abo abalina obukyayi mu nkola eya renin-antonsysten system (raS desipensir) oba endwadde ezireetebwa okusaasaanyiza agitensin II za waggulu.
